name: Abstract
description: Summary of a publication, usually without the full text.

name: Audiovisual Material
description: Audio or video materials like documentaries, films, etc.

name: Ancient Text
example: Translation of an ancient Greek manuscript.

name: Art Work
description: Art piece such as a painting or sculpture.

name: Book Chapter
example: Chapter on bioethics in a medical book.

name: Conference Paper
example: AI research paper at a symposium.

name: Generic
example: Default when no other type fits.

name: In Press
description: Accepted for publication, not yet published.

name: Journal (Full)
example: Full issue of a scientific journal.

name: Newspaper Article
example: The New York Times news report.
